title: Roads of Russia 5.32 garmin map gmapsupp unlocked
description:
Electronic vector map of Russia for garmin GPS navigators. Garmin "gmapsupp.img" map 
file container. Unlocked. There is a two variants of map: FID 1868 and FID 4941.

Warning! 
1)Your Garmin navigator must understand garmin NT map format and must support map files larger than 2 GB.
2) This is a map of automobile roads. If you need topo map, use Roads of Russia topo version.
